OL,6,FRipley's Believe It Or Not! has said
OL,7,Fit is "flush with excitement" after
OL,8,Fbuying a solid gold toilet for $12.1
OL,9,Fmillion US dollars (#9.3 million) at
OL,10,Fauction.
OL,12,FAn edition of the fully functioning
OL,13,Ftoilet from Maurizio Cattelan was
OL,14,Finstalled at the Solomon R Guggenheim
OL,15,FMuseum in New York in 2016 for a year,
OL,16,Fwith visitors encouraged to use the
OL,17,Ftoilet as they would any other.
