OL,6,FThe first casting was later stolen
OL,7,Ffrom Blenheim Palace in 2019 after a
OL,8,Fgang of thieves smashed their way in
OL,9,Fto the stately home and ripped out the
OL,10,Ffully functioning 18-carat gold toilet
OL,11,Fduring a raid.
OL,13,FRipley's has bought the only surviving
OL,14,Fedition of the 101.2kg toilet, titled
OL,15,FAmerica, at Sotheby's Now And
OL,16,FContemporary Evening Auction 2025.
