OL,3,CRipley's 'flush with excitement' after
OL,4,Cbuying gold toilet worth #9.3m
OL,6,FA social media post on the official
OL,7,FRipley's account said: "This World
OL,8,FToilet Day, we're flush with
OL,9,Fexcitement! Ripley's Believe It Or
OL,10,FNot! has purchased a solid gold toilet
OL,11,Ffor $12.1 million!
OL,13,F"Created by artist Maurizio Cattelan,
OL,14,Fthe solid gold toilet titled America
OL,15,Fis now the most valuable exhibit to
OL,16,Fjoin the Ripley's collection.
OL,18,F"The 18-carat throne first dazzled
OL,19,Fvisitors at the Guggenheim in 2016
OL,20,Fbefore disappearing in 2019 from
OL,21,FBlenheim Palace in an overnight caper.
