OL,6,F"Believe It Or Not!, that edition is
OL,7,Fstill missing! Ripley's has purchased
OL,8,Fthe only fully fabricated edition of
OL,9,Fthe golden throne still known to
OL,10,Fexist, and we intend to keep this one
OL,11,Ffrom embarking on any unexpected
OL,12,Fadventures.
OL,14,F"Ripley's plans to display the
OL,15,Fsculpture in all its glory, giving
OL,16,Fguests the chance to get up close to
OL,17,Fthe world's most extravagant restroom
OL,18,Ffixture.
